{"about_the_game":"<i>&quot;Welcome to Tower INC, the new courier! We have built for ourselves the tallest building in the city, so our employees do not feel the need to leave the cozy office for any trifles. Our performance indicators only grow every year. We get these results thanks to your delivery department. We expect a lot from your work and give you a lot. Do not let us down, comfortable and non-stop work of the entire corporation depends on you. Welcome to Tower INC!&quot; <br>- your biggest Boss</i><br><br>Start your career in the tallest skyscraper in the city and become a key figure in history. Fight overwhelming enemy forces, look for workarounds and solve puzzles to make your way to freedom. Walk through office spaces, tech floors, and other incredible locations such a large and complex building can have.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Vertical travel</strong> - the skyscraper is very high and you have to overcome many floors before you leave the building.<br></li><li><strong>Many enemies</strong> - the building is filled with enemies, and there are very few allies and safe places, besides, they are hunting for you, do not let enemies drive you into a corner.<br></li><li><strong>Puzzles</strong> - there will be tasks on your way that cannot be solved with weapons, be prepared for this. Perhaps some of the things that are lying around on the level can help you with this.<br></li><li><strong>Platforms</strong> - there are a lot of places in the skyscraper to fall from. Be careful.<br></li><li><strong>Inventory</strong> - prepare bigger pockets to fit more items.<br></li><li><strong>Interaction</strong> - in a skyscraper there are not only doors that need to be opened, but also many objects with which you need to interact.<br></li><li><strong>Variability</strong> - problems encountered on the way can be solved in several ways. Find a convenient one for yourself.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta