. Perhaps some of the things that are lying around on the level can help you with this.<br></li><li><strong>Platforms</strong> - there are a lot of places in the skyscraper to fall from. Be careful.<br></li><li><strong>Inventory</strong> - prepare bigger pockets to fit more items.<br></li><li><strong>Interaction</strong> - in a skyscraper there are not only doors that need to be opened, but also many objects with which you need to interact.<br></li><li><strong>Variability</strong> - problems encountered on the way can be solved in several ways. Find a convenient one for yourself.</li></ul>","developers":["JooGray videogames"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1464420/header.jpg?t=1665983462","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256809538,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256809538/movie480.mp4?t=1605349185","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256809538/movie_max.mp4?t=1605349185"},"name":"Tower early access trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256809538/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1605349185","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256809538/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1605349185","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256809538/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1605349185"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256807769,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256807769/movie480.mp4?t=1604559133","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256807769/movie_max